.nme.com/news/music/kiss-of-life-debut-ep-shhh-music-video-release-3465470">主打歌《Shhh》</a>首次亮相。该唱片还包括每位成员的独唱歌曲，其中 Belle 发行了自己创作的歌曲“Countdown”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-of-life-belle-cover-ariana-grande-honeymoon-avenue-3570768">《Hear KISS OF LIFE》的 Belle 翻唱 Ariana Grande 的《Honeymoon Avenue》</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 The Weeknd 的《Blinding Lights》成为 Spotify 上首首突破 40 亿次播放量的歌曲https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-first-song-ever-to-hit-four-billion-streams-on-spotify-3570777?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=the-weeknds-blinding-lights-成为 Spotify 上第一首突破 40 亿流的歌曲Will RichardsMon, 15 Jan 2024 08:32:44 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopSpotify https://www.nme.com/?p=3570777 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="周末" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>有史以来最热门的流行歌曲之一继续打破记录</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-first-song-ever-to-hit-four-billion-streams-on-spotify-3570777">The Weeknd 的《Blinding Lights》成为 Spotify 上第一首播放量达到 40 亿次的歌曲，并</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="周末" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/the-weekend-live-monterrey-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weekend">The Weeknd</a>的热门单曲《Blinding Lights》成为历史上第一首在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/spotify">Spotify</a>上播放量达到 40 亿次的歌曲。</p><p> 2023 年初透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-spotifys-most-streamed-song-of-all-time-3372843">Spotify 有史以来播放量最高的歌曲</a>出现在 Abel Tesfaye 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">《After Hours》</a>专辑中。它于 2019 年底发布，在排行榜上停留了 100 多周。</p><p>在那段时间里，它创下了排行榜前五名（43周）、前十名（57周）和前40名（86周）的最多周数的新纪录，并取代了 Chubby Checker 1960 年的热门单曲《The Twist》，成为最大单曲。美国告示牌有史以来最热门的 100 张单曲。</p><p> 《The Weeknd》在一份关于突破 40 亿大关的声明中表示：“我永远不会因为自己创造的任何东西惠及数百万人而感到谦卑，更不用说数十亿人了！</p><p> “我非常感谢这首歌让人们有一种感觉，让他们不断地回去听。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Weeknd - 炫目灯光（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4NRXx6U8ABQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>去年，《The Weeknd》对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>成为唯一一位拥有 1 亿 Spotify 听众的音乐艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-reacts-to-taylor-swift-becoming-only-other-artist-with-100million-spotify-listeners-3492773">的消息做出了回应</a>。</p><p>斯威夫特成为第一位达到这一里程碑的女艺人，目前仍位居流媒体服务上月听众人数最多的 The Weeknd 之后，超过 1.1 亿。</p><p>去年夏天，The Weeknd 又打破了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-breaks-wembley-stadium-ticket-sales-record-3486018">温布利球场最高上座率</a>纪录。 <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwGo2cgo5lj/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Live Nation UK</em></a>首先强调了这一消息，该公司宣布这位多次获得格莱美奖的艺术家“打破了温布利体育场传统音乐会布置的销售记录”。这次约会是他正在进行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-adds-wembley-stadium-date-to-after-hours-til-dawn-tour-3366891">“After Hours &#39;Til Dawn”巡演</a>的一部分。</p><p>就在上个月，这位艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-breaks-london-stadium-attendance-record-on-after-hours-til-dawn-tour-3469047">在伦敦体育场的两晚演出中打破了另一项最高上座率记录</a>，总共吸引了 16 万名粉丝。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-blinding-lights-becomes-first-song-ever-to-hit-four-billion-streams-on-spotify-3570777">The Weeknd 的《Blinding Lights》成为 Spotify 上第一首播放量达到 40 亿次的歌曲，并</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
